title: Vodafone Email Log in no longer works with Firefox
content:
Hi everybody and thanks for support in advance.

I can no longe log in and open my vodafone account (emails) with Firefox. Vodavone tells me to try another browser, it works fine with Microsoft Edge. I still want to use Firefox, what can I do?

Thank you and kind regards.
creator: h.kaser

title: avrei voluto scaricare della musica ma mi dice di convalidare l'età del browser ma non riesco a trovare dove
content: Salve, ho provato a scaricare della musica su YouTube, utente DvdVideoSoft [.] com, ma non me la fa scaricare perchè mi dice che il Contenuto è riservato (per la musica???) e di convalidare l'età del Browser, ma non riesco a trovare dov'è questo campo. Cosa posso fare? Grazie Umberto Trinca
creator: trincaumberto

title: Issue rendering animated SVG
content:
This has perplexed me for over a year at this point. The only page I have run into this issue on is https://create-react-app.dev/docs/getting-started and the animated SVG, but I imagine it would occur elsewhere if I ever ran into animated SVGs. Rather than try to describe it, I have included a screenshot of what I see (screencap is just a single frame, of course)

It animates, but it's like it is offset or only renders every other line or something. I don't know if this is the right place for this, but thought I'd try. Here are some browser specs:

title: My Website Not Reloading in Firefox
content:
Hi there,

I'm experiencing an issue where my website, "https://oceanofpdf.co.uk/", is not reloading properly in Firefox. When I try to refresh the page, it either hangs or doesn't display the updated content. This problem seems specific to Firefox, as the website works fine on other browsers like Chrome and Edge.

I've cleared my cache, tried private browsing mode, and even disabled all add-ons, but the problem persists. Could anyone help me figure out what might be causing this issue and how to resolve it? Any insights or troubleshooting steps would be greatly appreciated.

Thanks in advance!
creator: oceanofpdfinfo
